dc_description_s: This data represents parks for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2025. [This dataset is intended to provide a comprehensive collection of the public land in Dane County, Wisconsin. The data is derived from the tax parcel data and updated at least twice a year. Some public lands have complex partnerships and boundaries. An effort is made to as accurately, as possible, depict the public access, but may not be correctly represented.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
